longBusinessSummary: The Hachijuni Bank, Ltd. provides various banking products and services. It accepts various deposits; and provides loan products. The company also offers insurance services. As of March 31, 2020, the company operated 151 branches in Japan; 1 overseas branch in Hong Kong; and 3 representative offices in Shanghai, Bangkok, and Singapore. The Hachijuni Bank, Ltd. was founded in 1877 and is based in Nagano, Japan.
